{"tid":969063,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 無意中發現貼 Code 自動有色","createTime":"2019-01-04T17:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T07:28:29.000Z","uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c55b2bb25aef447f86f0c741e62ed6f06bd3e1b","tid":969063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"廢話少講, 先上圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOwgNB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOwgNB2.png&h=0868063b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人都有開 Google Sheet 儲 Code 習慣, 有時當私人字典咁望下查下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖說扯落去 notepad++ 會自動有色, 但喺街望兩望又唔想搞咁多野.. <br />\n無意中發現有個方法可以整到無論你貼咩都好, by default double quote 就自動綠色, integer 就藍色, slash 就去紅色, 起碼好睇少少<br />\n<br />\n點做?:<br />\n1. Copy 條你條 Code<br />\n2. 喺 Google Sheet 個 cell 入面打 = 然後 Ctrl V 貼上條 code<br />\n3. 返番最頭 delete 返個 = <br />\n4. Undo<br />\n條 code 就會自動有色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n懶閪版:<br />\n=<br />\nCtrl + V<br />\nCtrl + Home<br />\nDelete<br />\nCtrl + Z<br />\nEnter<br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441aca8708b03c61f6e3c4d6e52778a70ef2a555","tid":969063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"btw 要用 chrome<br />\n其他browser 冇試<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋應該係 google sheet formula bug 黎<br />\n應該遲下唔知邊個build 就會fix 返<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913e69160e6375396f469351f0568c9d80309b7a","tid":969063,"uid":147629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"其實喺editor（最少vscode/Xcode係work）到ctrl c/ctrl v去gdoc/word到都會連埋啲linting，重有得set content page，點解要咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf00d55237aa48c6613b8bb6fd55da88e4e4822","tid":969063,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T18:21:08.000Z","msg":"喺街睇code有咩好處"},{"pid":"46266128c0fa402731d99676c967230266fdcf73","tid":969063,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1M9fmo1WAFVK0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1M9fmo1WAFVK0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=002f7c70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e37e07720914c42bde45b2e6d19a5eb381d1e26","tid":969063,"uid":12599,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"有colab 有 gitlab 有markdown唔用, 用google sheet<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fb39888e3c15b1459b4fbddc1f0c9073c973d2","tid":969063,"uid":23953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"轉成圖咪有色lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}